<L>And turn my <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="AELD" EXTENT="2 letters">ght undaunted on the tomb?</L>
</LG>
<LG>
<L>With joy,&mdash;with grief, that healing hand I &s;ee;</L>
<L>Ah! too con&s;picuous! It is fix'd on high.</L>
<L>On high?&mdash;What means my phrenzy? I bla&s;pheme;</L>
