<L>The &s;kies it form'd; and now it bleeds for me&mdash;</L>
<L>But bleeds the balm I want&mdash;yet &s;till it bleeds;</L>
<L>Draw the dire &s;teel&mdash;Ah no!&mdash;the dreadful ble&s;&s;ing</L>
<L>What heart or can &s;u&s;tain, or dares forego?</L>
<L>There hangs all human hope; that nail &s;upports</L>
<L>The falling univer&s;e: That gone, we drop;</L>
