<L><PB N="59" REF="015714_0064_0F99DC79A85539D0">
Sen&s;ations new in angels bo&s;oms ri&s;e;</L>
<L>Su&s;pend their &s;ong; and make a pau&s;e in bli&s;s.</L>
</LG>
<LG>
<L>O for their &s;ong to reach my lofty theme!</L>
<L>In&s;pire me, night! with all thy tuneful &s;pheres;</L>
<L>Whil&s;t I with Seraphs &s;hare &s;eraphic themes,</L>
