<L>Could labour &s;uch expedient from de&s;pair</L>
<L><PB N="60" REF="015714_0065_0F99DC7ACE646320">
And re&s;cue both? Both re&s;cue! Both exalt!</L>
<L>O how are both exalted by the deed!</L>
<L>The wond'rous deed! or &s;hall I call it more?</L>
<L>A wonder in omnipotence it&s;elf!</L>
<L>A my&s;tery, no le&s;s to Gods than men!</L>
</LG>
<LG>
<L>Not, thus, our infidels th' eternal draw,</L>
<L>A God all o'er, con&s;ummate, ab&s;olute,</L>
<L>Full-orb'd, in his whole round of rays compleat:</L>
