<L>Lift up your <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="AELD" EXTENT="1 letter">eads, ye everla&s;ting gates!</L>
<L>And give the King of glory to come in:</L>
<L>W<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="AELD" EXTENT="2 letters"> is the King of glory? He who left</L>
<L>His throne of glory, for the pang of death:</L>
