</LG>
<LG>
<L>Where am I rapt by this triumphant theme,</L>
<L>On chri&s;tian joy's exulting wing, above</L>
<L>Th' Aonian mount?&mdash;Alas, &s;mall cau&s;e for joy</L>
<L>What if to pain immortal? If extent</L>
<L>Of being, to preclude a clo&s;e of woe?</L>
