</LG>
<LG>
<L>Bound, ev'ry heart! and, ev'ry bo&s;om, burn!</L>
<L>Oh what a &s;cale of miracles is here!</L>
<L>Its lowe&s;t round, high-planted on the &s;kies;</L>
