</LG>
<LG>
<L>So dear, &s;o due to heav'n, &s;hall prai&s;e de&s;cend,</L>
<L>With her &s;oft plume (from plau&s;ive angels wing</L>
<L>Fir&s;t pluck'd by man) to tickle mortal ears,</L>
<L>Thus diving in the pockets of the great?</L>
