<L>Shall prai&s;e her odours wa&s;te on virtue's dead,</L>
<L>Embalm the ba&s;e, perfume the &s;tench of guilt,</L>
<L>Earn dirty bread by wa&s;hing Ethiops fair,</L>
<L>Removing filth, or &s;inking it from &s;ight.</L>
