<L>How is night's &s;able mantle labour'd o'er,</L>
<L>How richly wrought with attributes divine!</L>
<L>What wi&s;dom &s;hines! what love! this midnight pomp&punc;</L>
<L>This go<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="AELD" EXTENT="1 letter">geous arch, with golden worlds inlay'd!</L>
<L>B<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="AELD" EXTENT="2 letters">it with divine ambition! nought to Thee;</L>
<L>For others this profu&s;ion: Thou, apart,</L>
