<LG>
<PB N="206" REF="015714_0213_0F99E288F08449C0">
<L>But the&s;e, thou think'&s;t, are gloomy paths to joy.&mdash;</L>
<L>True joy in &s;un&s;hine ne'er was found at fir&s;t;</L>
