<L>'Tis the&s;e, fir&s;t, give, then guard, a chearful heart.</L>
<L>Nought that is right, think little; well aware,</L>
<L>What rea&s;on bids, God bids; by his command</L>
<L>How aggrandiz'd, the &s;malle&s;t thing we do!</L>
<L>Thus, nothing is in&s;ipid to the wi&s;e;</L>
