<LG>
<L>" Mad! (thou reply'&s;t, with indignation fir'd)</L>
<L>" Of antient &s;ages proud to tread the &s;teps,</L>
<L>" I follow nature."&mdash;Follow nature &s;till,</L>
<L>But look it be thine own: is con&s;cience, then,</L>
