</LG>
<LG>
<L>Yet this &s;elf-love LORENZO makes his choice;</L>
<L>And, in this choice triumphant, boa&s;ts of joy.</L>
<L>How is his want of happine&s;s betray<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="AELD" EXTENT="1 letter">d,</L>
<L>By di&s;affection to the pre&s;ent hour!</L>
<L>Imagination wanders far afield:</L>
<L>The future plea&s;es: why? the pre&s;ent pains.&mdash;</L>
<L>"But that's a &s;ecret."&mdash;Yes, which all men know;</L>
<L>And know from thee, di&s;cover'd unawares.</L>
<L>Thy cea&s;ele&s;s agitation, re&s;tle&s;s roll</L>
<L>From cheat to cheat, impatient of a pau&s;e;</L>
<L>What is it?&mdash;'Tis the cradle of the &s;oul,</L>
<L>From in&s;tinct &s;ent, to rock her in di&s;ea&s;e,</L>
