<LG>
<L>Full well it might! I quite mi&s;took my road.</L>
<L>Born in an age more curious than devout;</L>
<L>More fond to fix the place of Heav'n, or Hell,</L>
<L>Than &s;tudious this to &s;hun, or that &s;ecure.</L>
