<L>That leads me to my point: LORENZO! know,</L>
<L>Without or &s;tar, or angel, for their guide,</L>
<L>Who wor&s;hip God, &s;hall find him. Humble love,</L>
<L><PB N="279" REF="015714_0286_0F99E2DE216A4A70">
And not proud rea&s;on, keeps the door of Heav'n;</L>
