<L><PB N="280" REF="015714_0287_0F99E2DF49E48FF0">
When beings, &s;o &s;uperior, homage boa&s;t,</L>
<L>And triumph in pro&s;trations to the throne?</L>
</LG>
<LG>
<L>But wherefore more of planets, or of &s;tars?</L>
