<L>Ten thou&s;and worlds, ten thou and ways devout,</L>
<L>All nature &s;ending incen&s;e to the throne,</L>
<L>Except the bold LORENZO's of our Sphere?</L>
<L>O <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="AELD" EXTENT="1 letter">ing he &s;olemn &s;ources of my &s;oul,</L>
<L>Since I <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="AELD" EXTENT="2 words"> like feign'd Eridanus,</L>
<L>My flowing numbers o'er the flaming &s;kies,</L>
<L>Nor &s;ee, of fancy, or of fact, what more,</L>
<L>Invites the mu&s;e&mdash;Here turn we, and review</L>
<L>Our pa&s;t nocturnal land&s;cape wide:&mdash;Then &s;ay,</L>
