<L><PB N="281" REF="015714_0288_0F99E2DFA74F9940">
" Ev'n this ackn<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="AELD" EXTENT="1 letter">wleg'd, leaves us &s;till in debt;</L>
<L>" If greater aught, that greater all is thine,</L>
