<L>" Who&s;e brea&s;t, capacious, can embrace, and lodge,</L>
<L>" Unburden'd, nature's univer&s;al &s;cheme;</L>
<L>" Can gra&s;p creation with a &s;ingle thought;</L>
<L>" Creation gra&s;p; and not exclude its Sire".&mdash;</L>
<L>To tell him farther&mdash;"It behoves him much</L>
<L>" To guard th' important, yet depending, fate</L>
<L>" Of being, brighter than a thou&s;and Suns:</L>
