<L>Behind the buckler of thine own right hand.</L>
</LG>
<LG>
<L>Fond man! the vi&s;ion of a moment made!</L>
<L>Dream of a dream! and &s;hadow of a &s;hade!</L>
<L>What worlds ha&s;t thou produc'd, what creatures fram'd,</L>
<L>What in&s;ects cheri&s;h'd, that thy God is blam'd?</L>
<L><PB N="303" REF="015714_0309_0F99E1907189C728">
When, pain'd with hunger, the wild Raven's brood</L>
<L>Calls upon God, importunate for food,</L>
