<L>They rage, they rend, their rav'nous jaws di&s;til</L>
<L><PB N="306" REF="015714_0312_0F99E192DED55B38">
With crim&s;on foam; and, when the banquet's o'er,</L>
<L>They &s;tride away, and paint their &s;teps with gore;</L>
